      "questionText": "A 64-year-old patient with a history of hypertension reports sudden chest tightness and shortness of breath. Vital signs: BP 88/58, HR 122, RR 26, SpO₂ 90%.\nWhat is the nurse's priority action?",
      "options": [
        {
